Tracking dependencies conflicts:

- project dependencies:

  https://solidsoft.wordpress.com/2014/11/13/gradle-tricks-display-dependencies-for-all-subprojects-in-multi-project-build/

  subprojects {
    task allDeps(type: DependencyReportTask) {}
  }



- tasks (buildscript) dependencies:

  https://solidsoft.wordpress.com/2016/06/07/gradle-tricks-display-buildscript-dependencies/


      ./gradlew buildEnvironment
